column6: How many dances would you like to be in?
column28: By auditioning for Dancers' Symposium, I am committing to a rehearsal time of one hour per week per dance that I am placed in, as well as participating in checkpoint, ticket sales, tech rehearsals, dress rehearsal, and the final show.  If I need to miss a rehearsal due to unavoidable circumstances, I will notify the choreographer in advance.  I will abide by all the rules of Dancers' Symposium Constitution and Policy Papers.  Being a dancer in this organization is a privilege and should I choose not to follow the guidelines outlined by the Constitution or should I drop out of a dance at some point during the semester, I accept that I will be placed on a one-semester probation from participating in Dancers' Symposium.  By signing below, I acknowledge that I have read and accepted these terms of participation in Dancers' Symposium.
